Resurrection Man #16
"Avenging Angels" part 1! The villainous Rider has taken over Mitch's immortal body and with it, sets out to have a hell of a time, leaving mass destruction in his wake. With his body occupied, Mitch finds himself being reborn into former lives in other eras. Continued in SUPERGIRL (Volume 4) #24.

Resurrection Man #17
"Avenging Angels" part 3, continued from SUPERGIRL (Volume 4) #24. The so-called angel Lament has come to collect Mitch's soul after his devastating battle with the Rider, but he'll have to do it over Supergirl's dead body--and Lament doesn't have a problem with that!
